      <title>美国银行的米德准备迎接蓝筹债券热潮的放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/bofa-s-mead-braces-for-a-slowdown-in-2024-blue-chip-bond-binge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行公司的丹·米德 (Dan Mead) 预计，美国蓝筹债券市场活动将在今年年底前放缓，因为借款人上半年大量借债，原因是目前受到诱人收益率的诱惑，同时为了避免以后的选举波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/bofa-s-mead-braces-for-a-slowdown-in-2024-blue-chip-bond-binge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:54:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
