      <title>德国最大工会推动工资上涨 7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/germany-s-largest-labor-union-pushes-for-7-boost-in-wages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国最大的工会要求为金属和电气零部件行业约 390 万名工人的工资增加 7%，以弥补过去几年消费者价格大幅上涨的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/germany-s-largest-labor-union-pushes-for-7-boost-in-wages</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:25:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
